name: Admin System UI Kit
description:
Hey Folks! I've been working on a lot of Admin and CMS modules at work lately. I created this little Admin UI Kit to optimise my workflow and improve my efficiency. This is not yet a comprehensive list. I'm planning to add updates to the components regularly.

Reach out to me on Twitter / Email / or let me know in the comments if I have missed any of the most frequently used components in the admin modules.
